data.description: Looking for a home in the beautiful Villas at Timber Run? Beautiful entry welcomes you into this neighborhood. As you cross over the bridge, look to your right/west for the beautiful clubhouse which has a fitness center and outdoor pool. This home has vaulted ceilings in all  major rooms. Sun room has windows on all three walls. The spacious great room boasts a gas fireplace and wood laminate flooring. Kitchen  comes complete with electric range, overhead microwave, dishwasher, refrigerator. Enjoy all your cabinet and countertop space plus the breakfast bar. Pendant lighting and pantry. Dining area.  Laundry room comes complete with your front loading washer and dryer and water softener. Primary bedroom with walk-in closet, full shower stall and spacious sink base for storage. Second bath has tub/shower combo. Two car attached garage.
